    "date": "2024-04-09T14:52:40Z",
    "text": "Senator Paul Simon Study Abroad Program Act of 2023\n\nThis bill expands access to study abroad for U.S. undergraduate students. It revises the Increase and Diversify Education Abroad for U.S. Students program (commonly known as the IDEAS program) and formally renames the program as the Senator Paul Simon Study Abroad Program."
